    icon: 'M1.5 8.67v8.58a3 3 0 003 3h15a3 3 0 003-3V8.67l-8.928 5.493a3 3 0 01-3.144 0L1.5 8.67z M22.5 6.908V6.75a3 3 0 00-3-3h-15a3 3 0 00-3 3v.158l9.714 5.978a1.5 1.5 0 001.572 0L22.5 6.908z',
